snippet.title: Quantum League - Cinematic trailer
snippet.description:
Quantum League is a revolutionary Time-Paradox Shooter: a competitive online FPS where you are battling within a time loop, tactically teaming up with your past and future selves in mind-blowing 1v1 and 2v2 matches. FREE OPEN BETA STARTS FEB 21ST: https://store.steampowered.com/app/1227800/Quantum_League__Free_Open_Beta/

Wishlist full game: https://store.steampowered.com/app/651150/Quantum_League/
